ZH: 今天我们要参加学校的赛跑比赛。
EN: Today we are going to participate in the school's running competition.

ZH: 他们赛跑的速度非常快。
EN: They run very fast in the race.

ZH: 赛跑不仅考验速度，还考验耐力。
EN: Running not only tests speed, but also endurance.

ZH: 这场赛跑比赛只有五公里。
EN: This running competition is only five kilometers.

ZH: 昨天的赛跑比赛很激烈。
EN: Yesterday's running competition was very intense.

ZH: 女孩子也可以参加赛跑比赛。
EN: Girls can also participate in running competitions.

ZH: 学生们在操场上赛跑比赛。
EN: Students are running races on the playground.

ZH: 我们要加强训练才能在赛跑中获胜。
EN: We need to train harder in order to win in the race.

ZH: 赛跑是一项很好的锻炼方式。
EN: Running is a great way to exercise.

ZH: 我们明天要晨跑，准备赛跑比赛。
EN: We are going for a morning run tomorrow to prepare for the running competition.

ZH: 赛跑比赛将在周末举行。
EN: The running competition will be held on the weekend.

ZH: 准备好了，开始赛跑！
EN: Ready, set, go for the race!

ZH: 赛跑需要集中注意力和全力以赴。
EN: Running requires focus and dedication.

ZH: 他是赛跑比赛的冠军。
EN: He is the champion of the running competition.

ZH: 擂台上只剩下两个选手进行赛跑比赛。
EN: There are only two competitors left on the platform for the running competition.

ZH: 我们每个人都能参加赛跑比赛。
EN: Everyone can participate in the running competition.

ZH: 赛跑比赛让我感到充满活力。
EN: Running competitions make me feel energized.

ZH: 赛跑比赛中，关键是保持坚持到底的精神。
EN: The key in a running competition is to keep the spirit of perseverance.

ZH: 赛跑比赛的终点在前面的房子那里。
EN: The finish line of the running competition is at the house in front.

ZH: 赛跑比赛是团队合作和个人表现的结合。
EN: Running competitions are a combination of teamwork and individual performance.
